<!-- 'level 1' ritual to purge world corruption -->
:: Gwylan Forest Journey Cancel
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<if $daily.gwylan.eventCancelled and $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 1 and !$willpowerSuccess>>
	You try to turn to leave, <<hypnosisText "but you quickly lose your train of thought. It's replaced by another. What else is there for you to do today? You're not busy. There's work to be done here.">>
	<br><br>

	Gwylan smiles sweetly. It makes your chest flutter.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Tell <<him>> you want to help (?:??)|Gwylan Forest Journey Prep]]>><<gwylanRequestEnd "skip">><<endevent>><<set $ritualForced to true>><</link>>
	<br>
<<else>>
	<<if $daily.gwylan.eventCancelled and $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 1>>
		<span class="green">You shake off the compulsion to go with Gwylan.</span>
	<</if>>
	<<He>> frowns. "Very well. Come back when you're ready."
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Next|Forest Shop Entrance]]>><<endevent>><<set $daily.gwylan.eventCancelled to true>><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>

:: Gwylan Forest Journey Prep
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<npc Gwylan>><<person1>>
<<set _hideRitualOptions to true>>
<<if !$gwylanSeen.includes("ritual_beast")>>
	You tell Gwylan that you're ready to help.
	<br><br>
<<elseif !$gwylanSeen.includes("ritual_sex_intro")>>
	You tell Gwylan that you want to help with <<his>> ritual.
	<br><br>
<<elseif !$ritualForced>>
	You tell Gwylan that you'd rather lure one of the forest's denizens for purging.
	<br><br>
<</if>>

<<if Time.isBloodMoon() or Time.monthDay is Time.lastDayOfMonth and Time.hour gte 16>>
	<<set _ritualFailSafe to true>><<unset $ritualForced>>
	<<He>> shakes <<his>> head. "Not now. Not on nights like tonight. It's too dangerous."
	<br><br>

	<<gwylanOptions>>
<<elseif Time.hour lte 8>>
	<<set _ritualFailSafe to true>><<unset $ritualForced>>
	<<set $daily.gwylan.ritualRequestBlocked to true>>
	<<He>> yawns. "Too early. Breakfast first.<<if $gwylan_cafe_intro>> Meet me at the cafe later?<</if>>"
	<br><br>

	<<gwylanOptions>>
<<elseif $worn.feet.type.includes("heels") and !$ritualForced>>
	<<set _ritualFailSafe to true>>
	<<He>> leans forward, looking down at your $worn.feet.name. "You'll break an ankle moving through the forest in those heels! Go grab a pair of proper shoes or boots," <<he>> scolds.
	<br><br>

	<<gwylanOptions>>
<<elseif $exposed gte 1 and !$ritualForced>>
	<<set _ritualFailSafe to true>><<unset $ritualForced>>
	<<He>> looks you over. "I'd recommend putting on some more clothes before we go."
	<br><br>

	<<gwylanOptions>>
<<elseif !isBeastSceneAllowed() and !$settings.plantsEnabled>>
	<<set _ritualFailSafe to true>><<unset $ritualForced>>
	<<He>> frowns. "You look nervous. We'll be dealing with the <span class="blue">natural denizens of the forest</span>, and you don't look prepared to come to terms with that. Try <span class="blue">opening your mind,</span> then come back.
	<br><br>

	<i><span class="blue">Beasts, monsterpeople or plantpeople must be enabled to continue.</span></i>
	<br><br>

	<<gwylanOptions>>
<<else>>
	<<set $beastRitual to {
		lure: "wolf",
		person: "Gwylan",
		difficultyMin: 550,
		difficultyMax: 850,
		binding: "none",
		petplay: 0,
		hasScent: false
	}>>
	<<if _gwylanTF.known>>
		<<set $beastRitual.difficultyMin += 150>><<set $beastRitual.difficultyMax += 300>>
	<</if>>
	<<if !$gwylanSeen.includes("ritual_beast")>>
		<<He>> clasps <<his>> hands together. "Wonderful! I'm excited, I can't remember the last time I had help with this. We'll be going deeper into the forest. By the end of the day, your curiosity should be sated."
	<<elseif $gwylanSeen.includes("struggles") and !$gwylanSeen.includes("ritual_sex_intro") and !_gwylanStatus.includes("cautious")>>
		<<He>> nods. "<span class="blue">There's something I want to talk to you about when we're done.</span> It can wait, though. Let me go get ready."
		<<He>> returns a few minutes later wearing a dark green belted tunic. Several bags, vials, and a sheathed knife adorn it.
		"Thanks for coming along. Let's go!"
	<<else>>
		<<He>> nods and heads to the back of the shop. "Give me a few minutes to get ready." <<He>> returns a few minutes later wearing a dark green belted tunic. Several bags, vials, and a sheathed knife adorn it.
		"Thanks for coming along. Let's go!"
	<</if>>
	<<if $ritualForced>>
		<<He>> pats you on the head. <<stress -1>><<lstress>>
	<</if>>
	<<unset $ritualForced>>
	<br><br>

	<<if $worn.feet.type.includes("heels")>>
		<<set _linebreak to true>>
		<<He>> glances down at your $worn.feet.name. "Take those off, you'll break an ankle running around the forest with those," <<he>> scolds.
		<<if $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 1>>
			<<hypnosisText "You follow <<his>> command, not wanting to disappoint <<him>>.">>
		<<else>>
			<<Hes>> probably right. You stow away your $worn.feet.name and decide to go barefoot.
		<</if>>
		<<feetundress "gwylanRitual">>
	<<elseif $worn.upper.type.includes("athletic") and $worn.lower.type.includes("athletic")>>
		<<set _linebreak to true>>
		<<He>> looks over your clothing. "Good choice, that looks easy to move around in."
		<<if $worn.feet.type.includes("rugged")>>
			<<He>> then glances down at your $worn.feet.name. "Those will hold up well in the forest, too."
		<</if>>
	<<elseif $worn.feet.type.includes("rugged")>>
		<<set _linebreak to true>>
		<<He>> leans forward, looking down at your $worn.feet.name. "Good choice, those will hold up well in the forest."
	<</if>>
	<<if $leftarm is "bound" or $rightarm is "bound" or $feetuse is "bound">>
		<<set _linebreak to true>>
		As <<he>> passes you by, <span class="green">you feel your bindings come loose.</span> "Can't have you running around like that."
		<<unbind>>
	<</if>>

	<<set _petplayChance to 0>>
	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("ritual_sex")>>
		<<if $worn.neck.name is "familiar collar" and $worn.neck.cursed is 1>>
			<<set _petplayChance to 100>>
		<<elseif _gwylanStatus.includesAny("dom", "lust")>>
			<<if $wolfgirl gte 6 or $cat gte 6 or $fox gte 6>>
				<<set _petplayChance += 20>>
			<</if>>
			<<set _petplayChance += Math.floor((C.npc.Gwylan.lust + C.npc.Gwylan.dom) / 2)>>
			<<if $worn.neck.collared is 1>>
				<<set _petplayChance += 20>>
				<<if $worn.neck.type.includes("leash")>>
					<<set _petplayChance += 10>>
				<</if>>
			<</if>>
			<<if $hypnosis_traits.devotion>>
				<<set _petplayChance += $hypnosis_traits.devotion * 10>>
			<</if>>
		<</if>>
	<</if>>
	<<if _petplayChance gte random(1, 100)>>
		<<if $worn.neck.name is "familiar collar" and $worn.neck.cursed is 1>>
			<<set _petplayOption to "command">>
			You feel your collar get tugged as your leash appears. "Does <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "my">> want a walk? <<gwylanCommand "Sit." 1>>"
			<<attach_leash true>><<set $beastRitual.leash to true>>
			<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("petplay")>>
			<<set _linebreak to true>>
		<<elseif $worn.neck.collared is 1>>
			<<set _petplayOption to "ask">>
			<<if $worn.neck.type.includes("leash")>>
				<<set $beastRitual.binding to "leash">>
				You feel a tug on your leash as Gwylan walks past you.
			<<else>>
				Gwylan stops and slips <<his>> hand along your collar as <<he>> walks by.
			<</if>>
			"Aww, you came prepared! Does <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "my">> want a walk?<<if !$worn.neck.type.includes("leash")>> I know I have some leashes lying around. It'll stop us from being separated again.<</if>>"
			<<if !$gwylanSeen.includes("petplay")>>
				You can't tell if <<hes>> joking.
			<</if>>
			<<if !$worn.neck.type.includes("leash")>>
				<<if !$gwylanSeen.includes("petplay")>>
					<<He>> begins to rummage around behind a shelf, which immediately tells you that <<he>> isn't.
				<<else>>
					<<He>> begins to rummage around behind a shelf.
				<</if>>
				A moment later <<he>> walks back up to you, and you hear a small click. <span class="lewd"><<Hes>> attached a leash to your collar.</span>
				<<attach_leash true>><<set $beastRitual.leash to true>>
			<<elseif !$gwylanSeen.includes("petplay")>>
				The look on <<his>> face turns seductive, which tells you that <<he>> isn't.
			<</if>>
			<<npcincr Gwylan lust 2>><<glust>>

			<<if _gwylanStatus.includesAny("dom", "lust")>>
				<<set _petplayOption to "command">>
				<br><br>
				<<He>> wraps the leash around <<his>> hand, pulling you a little closer.
				"<<gwylanCommand "Sit." 1>>"
			<</if>>
			<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("petplay")>>
			<<set _linebreak to true>>
		<<elseif !$worn.neck.cursed>>
			<<set _petplayOption to "ask">>
			<<set $beastRitual.binding to "leash">>
			<<if $worn.neck.name is "naked">>
				You feel something click around your neck.
			<<else>>
				You feel your $worn.neck.name lift away, and hear a click as something takes its place.
				<<neckundress "gwylanRitual">>
			<</if>>
			<span class="lewd">It's a collar with a leash.</span> It looks very well cared for. You're gently tugged by it. "Come on, <<pcpetname "Gwylan">>, it's time for a walk!" <<He>> giggles.
			<<neckwear 21>><<set $beastRitual.collared to true>>

			<<if _gwylanStatus.includesAny("dom", "lust")>>
				<<set _petplayOption to "command">>
				<br><br>

				<<He>> wraps the leash around <<his>> hand, pulling you a little closer.
				"But first... <<gwylanCommand "sit." 1>>"
			<<else>>
				"I can't have us getting separated again."
			<</if>>
			<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("petplay")>>
			<<set _linebreak to true>>
		<</if>>
	<</if>>
	<<if _linebreak>><br><br><</if>>

	<<if _petplayOption is "command">>
		<<link [[Sit|Gwylan Forest Journey Pet]]>><<set $phase to 1>><</link>>
		<br>
		<<link [[Stay standing|Gwylan Forest Journey Pet]]>><<set $phase to 2>><</link>><<gwylanWillpowerDifficulty>>
		<br>
		<<if $wolfgirl gte 6>>
			<<link [[Sit and beg like a dog|Gwylan Forest Journey Pet]]>><<sub 1>><<set $phase to 3>><<npcincr Gwylan lust 2>><</link>><<wolfgirl>><<glust>>
			<br>
		<<elseif $cat gte 6>>
			<<link [[Roll over and stretch like a cat|Gwylan Forest Journey Pet]]>><<sub 1>><<set $phase to 3>><<npcincr Gwylan lust 2>><<transform cat 1>><</link>><<cat>><<glust>>
			<br>
		<<else>>
			<<link [[Sit and beg like a dog|Gwylan Forest Journey Pet]]>><<sub 1>><<set $phase to 3>><<npcincr Gwylan lust 2>><</link>><<deviant1>><<glust>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
	<<else>>
		<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("romance") or C.npc.Gwylan.dom gte random(20, 100) and $gwylanSeen.includes("forest_journey_handheld")>>
			<<if $beastRitual.binding is "leash">>
				<<set $beastRitual.binding to "both">>
				<<He>> holds your leash with one hand, and takes your hand in <<his>> other. <<He>> leads you out of the shop and into the forest. <<takeHandholdingVirginity "Gwylan" "consensual">>
			<<else>>
				<<set $beastRitual.binding to "handheld">>
				<<He>> takes your hand in <<his>> as <<he>> leads you out of the shop and into the forest. <<takeHandholdingVirginity "Gwylan" "consensual">>
			<</if>>
		<<elseif $beastRitual.binding is "leash">>
			<<He>> pinches your cheek. "Stay close, <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "simple">>." You leave the shop, and head out into the forest with <<him>>, led by your leash.
		<<else>>
			<<He>> pinches your cheek. "Stay close, I don't want you getting lost." You leave the shop, and head out into the forest with <<him>>.
		<</if>>
		<br><br>

		<<link [[Walk silently|Gwylan Forest Journey 2]]>><<pass 20>><<set $phase to 1>><</link>>
		<br>
		<<if !$gwylanSeen.includes("ritual_beast")>>
			<<link [[Ask <<him>> for details on what you'll be doing|Gwylan Forest Journey 2]]>><<pass 20>><<set $phase to 2>><</link>>
		<<else>>
			<<link [[Chat while walking|Gwylan Forest Journey 2]]>><<pass 20>><<set $phase to 3>><</link>>
		<</if>>
		<br>
		<<if $beastRitual.binding isnot "handheld">>
			<<link [[Take <<his>> hand|Gwylan Forest Journey 2]]>><<pass 20>><<set $phase to 4>><<if C.npc.Gwylan.dom lt 10>><<npcincr Gwylan dom 1>><</if>><</link>><<if C.npc.Gwylan.dom lt 10>><<gyearning>><</if>><<handholdingvirginitywarning>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
		<<if _petplayOption is "ask">>
			<<if hasSexStat("deviancy", 2)>>
				<<link [[Let <<him>> walk you like a dog|Gwylan Forest Journey 2]]>><<sub 1>><<pass 20>><<set $phase to 5>><<npcincr Gwylan lust 2>><</link>><<glust>><<deviant2>>
				<br>
			<<else>>
				<<insufficientStat "deviancy" "to let <<him>> walk you like a dog">>
			<</if>>
		<</if>>
	<</if>>
<</if>>

:: Gwylan Forest Journey Pet
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<set $beastRitual.binding to "leash">>
<<if $phase is 1 or $phase is 2 and $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 1 and !$willpowerSuccess>>
	/* Sit */
	<<if $phase is 2 and $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 1 and !$willpowerSuccess>>
		<<set $beastRitual.disobey to true>>
		You try to resist the compulsion. <<gwylanHypnoName "cap">>'s smile shallows ever so slightly, and it <span class="red">fills you with guilt</span>.
		<<hypnosisText "Your knees buckle, and you stumble into sitting.">>
		<br><br>

		"<<pcPetname "Gwylan" "bad">>, trying to resist me. I might need to punish you for that." <<He>> pats you on the head. <<if $phase is 1 and $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 1>><<trauma -2>><<ltrauma>><</if>>
	<<else>>
		<<set $beastRitual.petplay++>>
		You sit on the floor of the shop.
		<br><br>

		"<<pcPetname "Gwylan" "good">>." <<He>> pats you on the head. <<if $phase is 1 and $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 1>><<trauma -2>><<ltrauma>><</if>>
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	"Come on, we have work to do." <<He>> pinches your cheek. "Stay close, <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "simple">>." You leave the shop, and head out into the forest with <<him>>, led by your leash.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Walk silently|Gwylan Forest Journey 2]]>><<pass 20>><<set $phase to 1>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Chat while walking|Gwylan Forest Journey 2]]>><<pass 20>><<set $phase to 3>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Take <<his>> hand|Gwylan Forest Journey 2]]>><<pass 20>><<set $phase to 4>><<if C.npc.Gwylan.dom lt 10>><<npcincr Gwylan dom 1>><</if>><</link>><<if C.npc.Gwylan.dom lt 10>><<gyearning>><</if>><<handholdingvirginitywarning>>
	<br>
	<<if hasSexStat("deviancy", 2)>>
		<<link [[Let <<him>> walk you like a dog|Gwylan Forest Journey 2]]>><<sub 1>><<pass 20>><<set $phase to 5>><<npcincr Gwylan lust 2>><</link>><<glust>><<deviant2>>
		<br>
	<<else>>
		<<insufficientStat "deviancy" "to let <<him>> walk you like a dog">>
	<</if>>
<<elseif $phase is 2>>
	/* Stay standing */
	<<if $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 1 and $willpowerSuccess>>
		You try to resist the compulsion. Gwylan's smile shallows ever so slightly, <span class="green">but you remain standing</span>.
	<<else>>
		You don't respond to Gwylan's command at all.
	<</if>>
	<<if C.npc.Gwylan.dom gte 50>>
		<<set $beastRitual.disobey to true>>
		<<He>> smiles again. "Ooh, being a <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "naughty">>? I'll have to think up a punishment for you," <<he>> says with a giggle as <<he>> tugs your leash. "Come on, we have work to do."
	<<else>>
		<<He>> frowns. "Fine. I'm still holding your leash, though. Come on, we have work to do."
	<</if>>
	<<He>> pinches your cheek. "Stay close, <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "simple">>." You leave the shop, and head out into the forest with <<him>>, led by your leash.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Walk silently|Gwylan Forest Journey 2]]>><<pass 20>><<set $phase to 1>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Chat while walking|Gwylan Forest Journey 2]]>><<pass 20>><<set $phase to 3>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Take <<his>> hand|Gwylan Forest Journey 2]]>><<pass 20>><<set $phase to 4>><<if C.npc.Gwylan.dom lt 10>><<npcincr Gwylan dom 1>><</if>><</link>><<if C.npc.Gwylan.dom lt 10>><<gyearning>><</if>><<handholdingvirginitywarning>>
	<br>
<<else>>
	/* Beast tf or deviancy petplay */
	<<set $beastRitual.petplay += 2>>
	<<if $wolfgirl gte 6>>
		You sit like a dog, placing your arms up against your chest as if you're begging.<<if $transformationParts.wolf.tail isnot "hidden">> Your tail wags behind you.<</if>> You stick your tongue out and pant, looking up to <<gwylanHypnoName>> with submission.
		<<He>> crouches down to your level, and starts to pet you.
	<<elseif $cat gte 6>>
		You sit, before flopping over and stretching out like a cat. <<gwylanHypnoName "cap">> crouches down and starts to scratch your <<bellyDescription>>.
	<<else>>
		You sit like a dog, and let out a mock bark. You place your arms up against your chest as if you're begging, looking up to <<gwylanHypnoName>> with submission.
		<<deviancy1>>
	<</if>>
	"Aww, who's my <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "good">>?" <<if $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 1>><<His>> touch fills you with bliss. <<stress -3>><<trauma -3>><<lstress>><<ltrauma>><</if>>
	<br><br>

	"I'd enjoy staying like this, but we have work to do." <<He>> whistles and tugs your leash.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Stand up and walk silently|Gwylan Forest Journey 2]]>><<pass 20>><<set $phase to 1>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Stand up and chat while walking|Gwylan Forest Journey 2]]>><<pass 20>><<set $phase to 3>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Stand up and take <<his>> hand|Gwylan Forest Journey 2]]>><<pass 20>><<set $phase to 4>><<if C.npc.Gwylan.dom lt 10>><<npcincr Gwylan dom 1>><</if>><</link>><<if C.npc.Gwylan.dom lt 10>><<gyearning>><</if>><<handholdingvirginitywarning>>
	<br>
	<<if hasSexStat("deviancy", 2)>>
		<<link [[Follow on all fours|Gwylan Forest Journey 2]]>><<sub 1>><<pass 20>><<set $phase to 5>><<npcincr Gwylan lust 2>><</link>><<glust>><<deviant2>>
		<br>
	<<else>>
		<<insufficientStat "deviancy" "to stay on all fours while following <<him>>">>
	<</if>>
<</if>>

:: Gwylan Forest Journey 2
<<set $outside to 1>><<set $location to "forest">><<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<if $worn.feet.type.includes("rugged") and $phase isnot 5>>
	<<set $beastRitual.difficultyMin -= 50>><<set $beastRitual.difficultyMax -= 50>>
<</if>>
<<if $phase is 1>>
	You stay quiet as you walk further into the forest. Gwylan marches forward, humming a tune.
	<br><br>

	<<He>> turns and faces you, now walking backwards. "You don't need to be so quiet. In fact, sometimes it's better to make a little noise. It'll keep the bears away." <<He>> turns back around.
<<elseif $phase is 2>>
	Gwylan marches forward, humming a tune.
	<br><br>

	<<switch $speech_attitude>>
		<<case "meek">>
			"Can you please tell me what we're doing now?" you ask.
		<<case "bratty">>
			"Alright, spit it out, what are we doing?" you ask.
		<<default>>
			"Are you going to keep being secretive?" you ask.
	<</switch>>
	<br><br>

	<<He>> turns and faces you, now walking backwards. "Tsk tsk, all the more curious! That's what I like about you. Be patient."
<<elseif $phase is 3>>
	You chatter with <<him>> as you walk through the forest. <<He>> does a lot of the talking, and you're fine listening.
<<elseif $phase is 4>>
	Gwylan marches forward, humming a tune.
	<br><br>

	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("forest_journey_handheld")>>
		You walk beside <<him>> and hold your hand out, grabbing one of <<hers>>. <<takeHandholdingVirginity "Gwylan" "consensual">> <span class="teal"><<He>> hesitantly squeezes yours back.</span>
	<<else>>
		<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("forest_journey_handheld")>>
		You walk beside <<him>> and hold your hand out, grabbing one of <<hers>>. <<takeHandholdingVirginity "Gwylan" "consensual">> <<He>> stops humming, but keeps walking. <span class="teal"><<He>> hesitantly squeezes your hand back.</span>
		<<if $beastRitual.binding isnot "leash">>
			"Good idea, we're less likely to get separated this way."
		<</if>>
		<<He>> starts humming again after a short while.
	<</if>>
	<<if $beastRitual.binding is "leash">>
		<<set $beastRitual.binding to "both">>
	<<else>>
		<<set $beastRitual.binding to "handheld">>
	<</if>>
<<else>>
	<<if $beastRitual.petplay is 2>>
		You remain on your hands and knees as you follow Gwylan out of the shop.
	<<else>>
		You get on your hands and knees, and follow Gwylan.
	<</if>>
	<<He>> doesn't seem to notice at first, humming a tune as <<he>> marches ahead. <<He>> turns and faces you, immediately coming to a stop.
	<<deviancy2>>

	<<He>> stares a moment, before giggling.
	<<if $beastRitual.petplay is 2>>
		"You're so eager." <<He>> crouches down and starts to pet you all over. "I like it. Keep being so good and maybe you'll get a treat later." <<He>> stands and tugs your leash again, and the two of you continue on.
		Your hands and knees quickly tire, so you stand up and walk the rest of the way.
	<<else>>
		"Aww, who's my <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "good">>?" <<He>> crouches down and starts to pet you all over. <<if $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 1>><<His>> touch fills you with bliss. <<stress -3>><<trauma -3>><<lstress>><<ltrauma>><</if>>
		<br><br>

		"I'd enjoy continuing, but we have work to do." <<He>> whistles and tugs your leash. You follow Gwylan on all fours.
	<</if>>
	<<set $beastRitual.petplay++>>
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<He>> leads you down a path that would be invisible if you weren't looking for it. The trees close in around you, and when you emerge, you're much deeper into the forest.
<br><br>

"It won't be much further now." <<He>> stops and kneels down,
<<if $beastRitual.binding is "both">>
