			The world swirls around <<gwylanHypnoName>>, and <<he>> both looks and smells like the perfect mate for you. <<if $beastRitual.petplay gte 3>>Your pet-like behavior seems to have put you in a strange mindset.<</if>> <<arousal 2000>><<gggarousal>>
		<<else>>
			<span class="blue">You're barely able to shake off the strange impulse.</span> <<arousal 500>><<garousal>>
		<</if>>
		</span>
	<</if>>
	<<hallucinogen 80>><<ghallucinogens>>
	<br><br>

	<<if $beastRitual.lure is "fox" and [_gwylanTF.ears, _gwylanTF.tail, _gwylanTF.fangs].includes("visible")>>
		<<npcincr Gwylan lust 2>>
		<<He>> cracks <<his>> neck, and when <<his>> eyes open, they're slightly dilated. "I'll race you there," <<he>> says, getting on all fours.
		<<if _gwylanTF.known>>
			<<His>> ears are perked, and <<his>> tail is puffed up.
		<<elseif $fox gte 6>>
			<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("gwylan_ears", "gwylan_tail", "gwylan_fangs")>>
			<br><br>

			You rub your eyes. From this position, Gwylan looks fox-like <<himself>>. Your vision blurs.
			<span class="pink">A set of mousy-brown fox ears sit atop <<his>> head, and a matching tail sways side to side behind <<him>>. Even <<his>> teeth look sharper.</span>
		<</if>>
		<<if $fox gte 6 and $beastRitual.lure is "fox" and _gwylanLovePercent gte 50>>
			<<if $beastRitual.lewdOption>>
				<span class="pink">Seeing <<him>> on all fours like this pushes your mating instincts to their limit.</span>
			<<else>>
				<span class="pink">Seeing <<him>> on all fours like this pushes you over the edge. <<He>> both looks and smells like the perfect mate.</span>
			<</if>>
			<<set $beastRitual.lewdOption to true>>
		<</if>>
	<<else>>
		"I'll race you there," <<he>> says, taking a few steps forward.
	<</if>>
<</if>>
"Come on!"
<<set $beastRitual.distance to 0>>
<<set $beastRitual.progress to 0>>
<<set $beastRitual.time to 0>>
<<if $beastRitual.binding is "handheld">>
	<<set $beastRitual.binding to "none">>
<</if>>
<<if $beastRitual.binding is "both" or $beastRitual.binding is "leash">>
	<<set $beastRitual.difficultyMin += 100>><<set $beastRitual.difficultyMax += 150>>
	<<He>> pulls you by your leash. The two of you dart off into the forest.
	<<set $beastRitual.binding to "leash">>
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Run with <<him>> (0:05)|Gwylan Forest Run Leashed]]>><<pass 5>><<tiredness 2>><<set $phase to "run">><</link>><<gtiredness>><<athleticsdifficulty $beastRitual.difficultyMin $beastRitual.difficultyMax true>>
	<br>
<<else>>
	<<set $beastRitual.distance to -1>>
	The two of you dart off into the forest. You lose track of each other almost immediately in the dense trees.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Race <<him>> (0:05)|Gwylan Forest Run]]>><<pass 5>><<tiredness 2>><<set $phase to "run">><</link>><<gtiredness>><<athleticsdifficulty $beastRitual.difficultyMin $beastRitual.difficultyMax true>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Just walk (0:10)|Gwylan Forest Run]]>><<stress -1>><<pass 10>><<set $phase to "walk">><</link>><<lstress>>
	<br>
<</if>>

:: Gwylan Forest Run Leashed
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<switch $beastRitual.progress>>
	<<case 0 1>>
		You are in the forest, racing Gwylan back to the shop. The trees are thick. You're still deep in. <<physique 1>>
	<<case 2 3>>
		You are in the forest, racing Gwylan back to the shop. <<physique 1>>
	<<default>>
		You're in the forest outskirts, racing Gwylan back to the shop. <<physique 1>>
<</switch>>
<br><br>

<<set $beastRitual.progress++>>
<<if $athleticsSuccess>>
	<<if $beastRitual.distance gte 1>>
		<<set $beastRitual.distance to 1>><<set _canBreakLeash to true>>
		You manage to keep your lead on Gwylan, <span class="blue">but the leash only lets you get so far ahead</span>.
	<<else>>
		<<set $beastRitual.distance++>>
		<<if $beastRitual.distance is 0>>
			<span class="green">You manage to catch back up to Gwylan.</span>
		<<else>>
			<span class="green">You manage to overtake Gwylan.</span> Your leash nearly goes taut.
		<</if>>
	<</if>>
<<else>>
	<<if $beastRitual.distance lte -1>>
		<<set $beastRitual.distance to -1>><<set _canTripGwylan to true>>
		You continue to struggle, <span class="blue">but the leash only lets you fall so far behind</span>. Gwylan is forced to slow down for you.
	<<else>>
		<<set $beastRitual.distance-->>
		<<if $beastRitual.distance is 0>>
			<span class="pink">Gwylan catches up to you.</span>
		<<else>>
			<span class="pink">Gwylan overtakes you.</span> Your leash nearly goes taut.
		<</if>>
	<</if>>
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<if $beastRitual.progress gte 6>>
	<span class="teal">You can see the shop through the trees. You're almost there!</span>
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Run! (0:05)|Gwylan Forest Run End]]>><<pass 5>><<tiredness 2>><<set $phase to "run">><</link>><<gtiredness>><<athleticsdifficulty $beastRitual.difficultyMin $beastRitual.difficultyMax true>>
	<br>
<<else>>
	<<cleareventpool>>

	<<if !$beastRitual.eventSkip>>
		<<addinlineevent "gwylan_forest_run_leashed_tree">>
			<<set _noOptions to true>>
			There's a thick cluster of trees up ahead, blocking most of the path.
			<<if $beastRitual.distance is 1>>
				<<set $phase2 to 0>>
			<<elseif $beastRitual.distance is -1>>
				Gwylan shifts to the <<if random(0,1)>><<set $phase2 to "left">><<else>><<set $phase2 to "right">><</if>> <span class="blue">$phase2</span>.
			<<else>>
				<<if random(0,1)>><<set $phase2 to "left">><<else>><<set $phase2 to "right">><</if>>
				Gwylan looks unsure of which way to go.
			<</if>>
			<br><br>

			<<link [[Dodge to the left|Gwylan Forest Run Leashed Trees]]>><<set $phase to "left">><</link>>
			<br>
			<<link [[Dodge to the right|Gwylan Forest Run Leashed Trees]]>><<set $phase to "right">><</link>>
			<br>
		<</addinlineevent>>
	<</if>>

	<<addinlineevent "gwylan_forest_run_leashed_hikers" 0.5>>
		<span class="lewd">You run past a pair of hikers.</span> They give you both strange looks.
		<br><br>
	<</addinlineevent>>

	<<addinlineevent "gwylan_forest_run_leashed_nothing">>
		/* Nothing */
	<</addinlineevent>>

	/* ToDo: Gwylan: More random events, can be flavour only  */

	<<runeventpool>>
	<<set $beastRitual.eventSkip to false>>

	<<if !_noOptions>>
		<<link [[Run (0:05)|Gwylan Forest Run Leashed]]>><<pass 5>><<tiredness 2>><<set $phase to "run">><</link>><<gtiredness>><<athleticsdifficulty $beastRitual.difficultyMin $beastRitual.difficultyMax true>>
		<br>
		<<if _canBreakLeash>>
			<<link [[Try to break free of the leash|Gwylan Forest Run Leashed Break]]>><<set $phase to "break">><</link>><<physiquedifficulty 4000 14000>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
		<<if _canTripGwylan>>
			<<link [[Stop and force Gwylan to release the leash|Gwylan Forest Run Leashed Stop]]>><<pain 5>><<set $phase to "stop">><</link>><<gpain>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
	<</if>>
<</if>>

:: Gwylan Forest Run Leashed Break
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<if $physiqueSuccess>>
	<<set $beastRitual.distance++>>
	You push forward with all your might. Gwylan holds the leash firmly, but is starting to stumble. You turn and grab the leash with both hands, yanking it. <span class="green">It flies out of <<his>> hands.</span>
	<br><br>

	<<He>> trips over <<himself>> with a look of surprise, and you keep running.
	<br><br>

	<<set $beastRitual.difficultyMin -= 100>><<set $beastRitual.difficultyMax -= 150>>

	<<link [[Run (0:05)|Gwylan Forest Run]]>><<pass 5>><<tiredness 2>><<set $phase to "run">><</link>><<gtiredness>><<athleticsdifficulty $beastRitual.difficultyMin $beastRitual.difficultyMax true>>
	<br>
<<else>>
	You push forward with all your might, but Gwylan pulls back just as hard. <span class="pink">You can't get enough leverage to break <<his>> grip on the leash.</span>
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Run (0:05)|Gwylan Forest Run Leashed]]>><<pass 5>><<tiredness 2>><<set $phase to "run">><</link>><<gtiredness>><<athleticsdifficulty $beastRitual.difficultyMin $beastRitual.difficultyMax true>>
	<br>
<</if>>

:: Gwylan Forest Run Leashed Stop
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<set $beastRitual.difficultyMin -= 100>><<set $beastRitual.difficultyMax -= 150>>
<<if $bodysize is 3>>
	<<set $beastRitual.distance++>>
	You stop. Gwylan doesn't. <span class="green">Due to your large body, <<he>> completely wipes out as <<he>> reaches the end of the leash's length, unable to pull you along.</span>
	<br><br>

	You run ahead of <<him>> as <<he>> recovers, and you catch <<him>> sticking <<his>> tongue out at you.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Run (0:05)|Gwylan Forest Run]]>><<pass 5>><<tiredness 2>><<set $phase to "run">><</link>><<gtiredness>><<athleticsdifficulty $beastRitual.difficultyMin $beastRitual.difficultyMax true>>
	<br>
<<else>>
	<<set $beastRitual.distance-->><<set $beastRitual.time++>>
	You stop. Gwylan doesn't. You stumble forward, landing on your hands and knees. <<He>> stumbles in turn thanks to the sudden weight at your end of the leash, <span class="teal">forcing <<him>> to drop it</span> as <<he>> continues running.
	<<He>> has more distance on you now, but at least you're not being pulled along anymore.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Run (0:05)|Gwylan Forest Run]]>><<pass 5>><<tiredness 2>><<set $phase to "run">><</link>><<gtiredness>><<athleticsdifficulty $beastRitual.difficultyMin $beastRitual.difficultyMax true>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Just walk (0:10)|Gwylan Forest Run]]>><<stress -1>><<pass 10>><<set $phase to "walk">><</link>><<lstress>>
	<br>
<</if>>

:: Gwylan Forest Run Leashed Trees
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<if $beastRitual.distance is 1>>
	You dodge to the $phase of the trees. Gwylan follows.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Run (0:05)|Gwylan Forest Run Leashed]]>><<set $beastRitual.eventSkip to true>><<pass 5>><<tiredness 2>><<set $phase to "run">><</link>><<gtiredness>><<athleticsdifficulty $beastRitual.difficultyMin $beastRitual.difficultyMax true>>
	<br>
<<else>>
	<<if $phase2 is "left" and $phase is "right" or $phase2 is "right" and $phase is "left">>
		<<if $beastRitual.distance is 0>>
			You dodge to the $phase of the trees. Unfortunately, Gwylan dodged in the opposite direction.
		<<else>>
			You dodge to the $phase of the trees, opposite Gwylan.
		<</if>>
		<span class="pink">Your leash snags in the thicket between you,</span> pulling both of you back and sending you tumbling as the leash snaps out of Gwylan's hand.
		<br><br>

		"Ouch! We should have communicated that better." <<He>> rubs <<his>> hand as <<he>> stands back up, offering you <<his>> other hand to help you up too.
		<br><br>

		You get your bearings. Gwylan starts running ahead again once <<he>> knows you're mostly unharmed. <span class="teal">You're free of the leash.</span>
		<br><br>

		<<set $beastRitual.difficultyMin -= 100>><<set $beastRitual.difficultyMax -= 150>>

		<<gwylanChaseOptions>>
	<<else>>
		You dodge to the $phase of the trees, following Gwylan.
		<br><br>

		<<link [[Run (0:05)|Gwylan Forest Run Leashed]]>><<set $beastRitual.eventSkip to true>><<pass 5>><<tiredness 2>><<set $phase to "run">><</link>><<gtiredness>><<athleticsdifficulty $beastRitual.difficultyMin $beastRitual.difficultyMax true>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
<</if>>
<<set $phase2 to 0>>

:: Gwylan Forest Run
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>><<set $beastRitual.binding to "none">>
<<switch $beastRitual.progress>>
	<<case 0 1>>
		You are in the forest, <<if $phase is "walk">>walking<<else>>racing Gwylan<</if>> back to the forest shop. The trees are thick. You're still deep in.
	<<case 2 3>>
		You are in the forest, <<if $phase is "walk">>walking<<else>>racing Gwylan<</if>> back to the forest shop.
	<<default>>
		You're in the forest outskirts, <<if $phase is "walk">>walking<<else>>racing Gwylan<</if>> back to the forest shop.
<</switch>>
<<if $phase is "run">>
	<<physique 1>>
	<<if $athleticsSuccess>>
		<<set $beastRitual.distance++>>
		<<if $beastRitual.foxChase>>
			You run with the grace of a fox, <span class="green">and manage to make good progress.</span>
		<<else>>
			You push yourself, <span class="green">and manage to make good progress.</span>
		<</if>>
	<<else>>
		<<set $beastRitual.time++>><<set $beastRitual.distance -= 1>>
		You push yourself, <span class="pink">but your pace is uneven and you're starting to get winded.</span>
	<</if>>
<<elseif $phase is "walk">>
	<<set $beastRitual.distance -= 2>><<set $beastRitual.time++>>
	<<set $beastRitual.difficultyMin -= 50>><<set $beastRitual.difficultyMax -= 50>>
	You take your time, saving your energy.
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<set $beastRitual.progress++>>

<<if $beastRitual.time gte 3 and $beastRitual.distance lte -1 and !$beastRitual.waited>>
	<<set _gwylanWaiting to true>>
	<<set $beastRitual.distance to 0>>
<</if>>

<<if $beastRitual.hasScent>>
	You can easily smell the tincture on Gwylan.
	<<if $beastRitual.distance lte -3>>
		<span class="pink"><<Hes>> far ahead of you.</span>
	<<elseif $beastRitual.distance lte -1>>
		<span class="purple"><<Hes>> just ahead of you.</span>
	<<elseif $beastRitual.distance gte 3>>
		<span class="green">You've left <<him>> in the dust.</span>
	<<elseif $beastRitual.distance gte 1>>
		<span class="teal"><<Hes>> a short distance behind you.</span>
	<<else>>
		<span class="blue">It smells like <<hes>> nearby, about the same distance from the shop as you are.</span> <<arousal 500>><<garousal>>
	<</if>>
<<elseif $fox gte 4>>
	Your fox-like instincts are sharp during the chase.
	<<if $beastRitual.distance lte -3>>
		<span class="pink">You can tell Gwylan is far ahead of you.</span>
	<<elseif $beastRitual.distance lte -1>>
		<span class="purple">You can tell Gwylan is just ahead of you.</span>
	<<elseif $beastRitual.distance gte 3>>
		<span class="green">You can tell you've left Gwylan in the dust.</span>
	<<elseif $beastRitual.distance gte 1>>
		<span class="teal">You can tell Gwylan is a short distance behind you.</span>
	<<else>>
		<span class="blue">It smells like Gwylan is nearby, about the same distance from the shop as you are.</span> <<arousal 500>><<garousal>>
	<</if>>
<<else>>
	<<if $beastRitual.distance is 0 and !_gwylanWaiting>>
		You hear someone running nearby. <span class="blue">Gwylan must be close.</span>
	<<else>>
		You've lost track of Gwylan.
	<</if>>
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<if _gwylanWaiting>>
	<<set $beastRitual.waited to true>>
	<<if $beastRitual.hasScent>>
		The scent suddenly becomes much stronger, as if it's coming back towards you.
	<<elseif $beastRitual.lewdOption>>
		You smell the serum that Gwylan applied to <<himself>>. <<He>> must be very close.
	<<else>>
		You hear rustling up ahead.
	<</if>>
	You stay low in the foliage and move to investigate.
	<br><br>

	You spot Gwylan in a small clearing, looking around with a concerned look on <<his>> face. <<His>> hands are clasped together near <<his>> chest.
	<br><br>

	<<He>> calls your name, but isn't looking in your direction. "Oh dear, oh dear, oh no no no! I hope <<pshe>> didn't get lost. I shouldn't have left <<phim>> so far behind."
	<br><br>

	<<if $beastRitual.lure is "fox" and $beastRitual.person is "player">>
		<span class="blue"><<His>> nose twitches. <<He>> turns and looks right at you.</span> <<He>> must be able to smell the fluid on you.
		<br><br>

		"Oh, thank goodness. I'm sorry for leaving you like that. It's not much further to the shop now, let's go!" <<He>> takes off again.
		<br><br>

		<<link [[Run (0:05)|Gwylan Forest Run]]>><<pass 5>><<tiredness 2>><<set $phase to "run">><</link>><<gtiredness>><<athleticsdifficulty $beastRitual.difficultyMin $beastRitual.difficultyMax true>>
		<br>
		<<link [[Walk (0:10)|Gwylan Forest Run]]>><<stress -1>><<pass 10>><<set $beastRitual.time++>><<set $phase to "walk">><</link>><<lstress>>
		<br>
	<<else>>
		<<if $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 1 and $beastRitual.petplay gte 2>>
			<<set _beckoned to true>>
			<<gwylanHypnoName "cap">> calls your name again, this time with the inflection of an owner searching for a lost pet. <span class="witchbloom">You feel a strange compulsion to reveal yourself and go to <<him>>.</span>
			<<set _linebreak to true>>
		<</if>>
		<<if $beastRitual.lewdOption>>
			<<if _linebreak>>
				However, you also
			<<else>>
				You
			<</if>>
			feel your mating instincts working some devilry. You have a strong urge to pounce on <<him>><<if _linebreak>>, too<</if>>.
			<<set _linebreak to true>>
		<</if>>
		<<if _linebreak>><br><br><</if>>

		<<link [[Use this opportunity to get ahead of <<him>>|Gwylan Forest Run Clearing]]>><<set $phase to "past">><</link>><<if _beckoned>><<gwylanWillpowerDifficulty>><</if>>
		<br>
		<<if _beckoned>>
			<<link [[Approach <<him>> like a lost pet|Gwylan Forest Run Clearing]]>><<sub 1>><<set $phase to "pet">><</link>><<if $beastRitual.petplay gte 3 and !$beastRitual.petplayHypno>><<gwylanHypnoNote>><</if>>
		<<else>>
			<<link [[Reveal yourself|Gwylan Forest Run Clearing]]>><<set $phase to "reveal">><</link>>
		<</if>>
		<br>
		<<if $beastRitual.lewdOption>>
			<<link [[Ambush|Gwylan Forest Run Ambush]]>><<def 1>><<transform fox 1>><</link>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
	<</if>>
<<elseif $beastRitual.progress gte 6>>
	<span class="teal">You can see the shop through the trees. You're almost there!</span>
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Run! (0:05)|Gwylan Forest Run End]]>><<pass 5>><<tiredness 2>><<set $phase to "run">><</link>><<gtiredness>><<athleticsdifficulty $beastRitual.difficultyMin $beastRitual.difficultyMax true>>
	<br>
	<<if !$beastRitual.foxChase>>
		<<link [[Walk (0:10)|Gwylan Forest Run End]]>><<stress -1>><<pass 10>><<set $phase to "walk">><</link>><<lstress>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
<<else>>
	<<if $phase is "run">>
		<<if $beastRitual.stalkedProgress isnot undefined>>
			<<set $beastRitual.stalkedProgress++>>
		<</if>>
	<<else>>
		<<if $beastRitual.stalkedProgress isnot undefined>>
			<<set $beastRitual.stalkedProgress += 3>>
		<</if>>
	<</if>>

	<<cleareventpool>>

	<<if $beastRitual.person is "player" and $beastRitual.stalked isnot "done" and $beastRitual.stalked isnot "howl">>
		<<switch $beastRitual.lure>>
			<<case "wolf">>
				<<if !$beastRitual.stalked>>
					<<addinlineevent "gwylan_forest_run_wolf_start">>
						<<set $beastRitual.stalked to "wolf">><<set $beastRitual.stalkedProgress to 0>>
						<span class="red">You hear a howl close by. A chill runs up your spine.</span>
						<br><br>
					<</addinlineevent>>
				<<elseif $beastRitual.stalkedProgress gte 3>>
					<<addinlineevent "gwylan_forest_run_wolf_lunge" 10>>
						<<endevent>><<beastNEWinit 1 wolf>>
						A <<beasttype>> lunges at you from the bushes!
						<br><br>

						<<if $monster is 1 or $settings.bestialityEnabled>>
							<<set _noOptions to true>>
							<<link [[Next|Gwylan Forest Run Attacked]]>><<set $molestationstart to 1>><</link>>
							<br>
						<<else>>
							<<bHe>> chases you through the woods. You run until you can no longer hear <<bhim>> behind you. You're not sure if you outran <<bhim>> or <<bhe>> grew bored.
							<<beastescape>><<gtiredness>><<tiredness 4>>
							<br><br>

							<<endevent>><<npc Gwylan>><<person1>>
						<</if>>
					<</addinlineevent>>
				<</if>>
			<<case "fox">>
				<<if !$beastRitual.stalked>>
					<<addinlineevent "gwylan_forest_run_fox">>
						<<set $beastRitual.stalked to "fox">>
						<<endevent>><<beastNEWinit 1 fox>><<person1>><<set _noOptions to true>>
						You spot a <<beasttype>> in the bushes just before <<bhe>> pounces!
						<br><br>

						<<link [[Dodge <<bhim>>|Gwylan Forest Run Fox]]>><<set $phase to "dodge">><</link>><<dancedifficulty 1 1000>>
						<br>
						<<link [[Redirect <<bhis>> pounce|Gwylan Forest Run Fox]]>><<set $phase to "redirect">><</link>><<physiquedifficulty 4000 16000>>
						<br>
						<<if $fox gte 4>>
							<<link [[Scream at <<bhim>>|Gwylan Forest Run Fox]]>><<set $phase to "scream">><<transform fox 1>><</link>><<fox>>
							<br>
						<<elseif $harpy gte 6>>
							<<link [[Screech at <<bhim>>|Gwylan Forest Run Fox]]>><<set $phase to "screech">><<transform bird 1>><</link>><<harpy>>
							<br>
						<</if>>
					<</addinlineevent>>
				<</if>>
			<<default>>

		<</switch>>
	<</if>>

	<<addinlineevent "gwylan_forest_run_nothing" 2>>
		/* Nothing */
	<</addinlineevent>>

	<<runeventpool>>

	<<if !_noOptions>>
		<<gwylanChaseOptions>>
	<</if>>
<</if>>

:: Gwylan Forest Run Howl
<<effects>>
<<set $beastRitual.stalked to "howl">>
You howl in return. In the shade of the trees, you spot multiple sets of eyes.
<<if $wolfgirl gte 6>>
	They look with hunger at first, but they also seem curious.
<<else>>
	They recognise their pack leader's voice, and follow at a distance.
<</if>>
You can tell they won't attack, <span class="lewd">but they might all follow you back to the shop</span>.
<br><br>

<<gwylanChaseOptions>>

:: Gwylan Forest Run Fox Chase
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
