<<set $beastRitual.difficultyMin -= 50>><<set $beastRitual.difficultyMax -= 50>>
You stop to sniff the air. You know you can find <<him>>.
<br><br>

Your senses focus in, and you dart after a set of tracks hidden in the overgrowth.
<br><br>

They're easy to follow, as if left by someone that wanted you to chase them. Your muscles and lungs are invigorated by the chase.
<br><br>

You'll be feeling this later, but you don't mind. Your heart pounds as you continue to bound through the forest.
<<if $hallucinations gte 1>>
	<span class="blue">It feels as though it yields to you, accepting you as one of its denizens. The space between the trees is just a little larger, and the ground provides slightly better traction.</span>
<</if>>
<br><br>

Finally, <span class="green">you see Gwylan running ahead of you.</span> You push yourself even harder and manage to catch up to <<him>>.
<<if _gwylanTF.known>>
