<<else>>
	<<He>> looks surprised, but grins. <<He>> leads you on a brief chase.
<</if>>
<br><br>

You're evenly matched with <<him>> for the moment. You quickly get separated again, but you're even more determined to beat <<him>> back to the shop now.
<br><br>

<<gwylanChaseOptions>>

