	"You want to share this burden with me?" <<He>> looks surprised, but slowly grows a bright smile. "That means more to me than you know. Thank you." <<gyearning>>
<<else>>
	<<switch $speech_attitude>>
		<<case "meek">>
			"L-let me take half."
		<<case "bratty">>
			"Let me help. I'm not asking."
		<<default>>
