<<set _stressFactor to $beastRitual.poisonAmount * 12>>
<<set _traumaFactor to $beastRitual.poisonAmount * 6>>
<<set _purityFactor to $beastRitual.poisonAmount * -25>>

<<if $beastRitual.lure is "dryad">>
	<<if !$gwylanSeen.includes("ritual_corruption_share_dryad")>>
		<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("ritual_corruption_share_dryad")>>
		<<He>> digs through the bucket for a moment. "Let me find you a crunchy one." After a moment, <<he>> pulls out a small blackened leaf and hands it to you.
		<br><br>

		It doesn't look too bad. You pop it in your mouth and start chewing.
		<br><br>

		<<if $fallenangel gte 2 and $fallenangel lt 4>>
			<span class="black">You taste nothing but the salt.</span> Gwylan watches you closely, waiting for a reaction.
			You turn to <<him>> and shrug.
			<br><br>

			<<He>> opens <<his>> mouth to say something, but ends up holding <<his>> tongue.
			<br><br>

			Despite being flavourless at first, a vile aftertaste starts to build up in the corners of your mouth. You gag involuntarily.
		<<elseif $demon gte 6>>
			It's not bad. In fact, <span class="purple">it's pretty tasty</span>. You reach for another one. <<stress -6>><<trauma -3>><<purity -10>><<lstress>><<ltrauma>><<lpurity>>
			<br><br>

			Gwylan doesn't stop you. "I suppose I should have expected that. Although, you should be warned that the aftertaste—"
			<br><br>

			The aftertaste hits you.
		<</if>>
		<span class="red">It is the single most vile thing you have ever tasted in your life.</span> Gwylan puts a hand over your mouth, and another on your back.
		"I'm sorry, but you can't spit it out." <<stress _stressFactor>><<purity -5>><<ggstress>><<lpurity>>
		<br><br>

		It's a struggle, but you manage to force yourself to swallow. Gwylan holds <<his>> hands over your mouth for another moment to be sure, but slowly releases you.
		<br><br>

		You gasp and heave. "You're telling me it's even worse without the salt?"
		<br><br>

		Gwylan nods sadly.
		<br><br>

		The two of you pick away at more of the tainted leaves for some time. "It doesn't taste quite as bad when shared. Thank you again."
	<<else>>
		You dig into the bucket.
		<<if $fallenangel gte 2 and $fallenangel lt 4>>
			<span class="black">Every bite is completely bereft of flavour or substance, save for the salt.</span>
			<br><br>

			<<if $transformationParts.fallenAngel.wings isnot "hidden">>
				Gwylan rubs your blackened wings. They twitch. They usually can't feel anything.
			<</if>>
			"Emptiness has value. Poetic irony."
		<<elseif $demon gte 6>>
			<span class="purple">You end up eating more of it than Gwylan does.</span> <<stress `(_stressFactor * -1)`>><<trauma `(_traumaFactor * -1)`>><<purity `(_purityFactor * 2)`>><<llstress>><<ltrauma>><<llpurity>>
			<br><br>

			<<if $transformationParts.demon.horns isnot "hidden" and $transformationParts.demon.tail isnot "hidden">>
				<<He>> strokes your horns. "Who's a good little imp?" Your tail wags in response. <<trauma -1>><<ltrauma>>
			<<else>>
				<<He>> pets your head. "You're wonderful, doing this for me." <<trauma -1>><<ltrauma>>
			<</if>>
		<<else>>
			<span class="red">Every bite is vile,</span> but you power through it. <<He>> deals with this every week. You can manage. <<stress _stressFactor>><<purity _purityFactor>><<ggstress>><<lpurity>>
			<br><br>

			Gwylan rubs your back. "You're doing a good thing for the world, and for me."
		<</if>>
	<</if>>
<<else>>
	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("ritual_corruption_share") and _gwylanLovePercent gte 75 and C.npc.Gwylan.dom gte 15 and $beastRitual.poisonAmount gte 2>>
		<<if !$gwylanSeen.includes("ritual_corruption_share_intimate")>>
			<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("ritual_corruption_share_intimate")>>
			You reach for the bowl, but Gwylan holds it away from you. "I... I know a way that it can be made more tolerable for both of us." <<His>> face becomes a bit more red.
			"The poison is released and spread through coitus, but carnality isn't the only vector of transmission." <<He>> pauses, trying to choose <<his>> next words carefully.
			<br><br>

			"There's a specific human connection that can dull the sting of absorption." <<He>> looks away. "Just... close your eyes and open your mouth, please."
			<br><br>

			You close your eyes, and open your mouth. Gwylan tilts your head back and cups your cheeks. A moment later, you feel the fluid trickling into your mouth.
			<br><br>

			You open your eyes.
			<br><br>

			<<His>> face is very close. <span class="pink">You're nearly kissing. The poison drips from <<his>> tongue onto yours. <<His>> eyes are closed, and <<he>> holds <<his>> hair aside with one hand.</span>
			<br><br>

			<<His>> eyes blink open when you've shared it all. <<His>> face is beetroot red, and <<he>> steps away from you. "There's power in intimacy, especially when used in conjunction with carnality.
			<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("romance")>>
				You're the only person I could bear do this with."
			<<elseif $gwylanSeen.includes("yearning")>>
				You've already broken that boundary, so there's no reason not to."
			<<else>>
				Don't take this the wrong way, though. It can't go further than this between us." <<He>> shifts side to side.
				<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("ritual_sex")>>
					"There's a difference between coitus and intimacy. It's already more than I'd be comfortable doing with anyone else."
				<<else>>
					"We can't be intimate with each other. It's already more than I'd be comfortable doing with anyone else."
				<</if>>
			<</if>>
		<<else>>
			Gwylan's face reddens a bit as <<he>> drinks all of the fluid, and brings <<his>> face close to yours. <<He>> cups your face, and you open your mouth.
			<br><br>

			<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("romance") or _gwylanStatus.includes("lust")>>
				<<He>> doesn't bother letting it drip, instead pulling you right into a kiss. You feel the fluid enter your mouth alongside <<his>> tongue. <<takeKissVirginity "Gwylan" "romantic">>
			<<else>>
				Your eyes half-close on their own as half of the poison drips down into your mouth.
			<</if>>
		<</if>>
		<<npcincr Gwylan dom 1>><<gyearning>>
		<br><br>

		You swallow it.
		<<if $angel gte 6>>
			<span class="gold">The purity within you quietly snuffs it out.</span><<stress -2>><<trauma `(Math.floor(_traumaFactor/2))`>><<lstress>><<gtrauma>>
		<<elseif $fallenangel gte 2 and $fallenangel lt 4>>
			<span class="black">It rushes to fill the emptiness inside of you, and for a moment, you don't feel so empty anymore.</span> <<ltrauma>><<trauma -2>>
		<<elseif $demon gte 6>>
			<span class="purple">It blissfully melds with your very being.</span><<stress `(_stressFactor * -2)`>><<trauma `(_traumaFactor * -2)`>><<purity `(_purityFactor * 2)`>><<llstress>><<ltrauma>><<lllpurity>>
		<<elseif $dryad gte 6>>
			<span cass="pink">You feel weak as it twists your connection to the world, but your roots, connected to Gwylan, endure.</span><<stress `(Math.floor(_stressFactor/2))`>><<trauma `(Math.floor(_traumaFactor/2))`>><<pain 5>><<gstress>><<gtrauma>><<gpain>>
		<<else>>
			<<purity _purityFactor>><<llpurity>>
		<</if>>
		<br><br>

		<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("romance") or _gwylanStatus.includesAny("dom", "lust")>>
			Gwylan sits next to you, and pulls your head down into <<his>> lap. <<He>> strokes your hair. "You're my <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "good">>." <<trauma -1>><<ltrauma>>
		<<else>>
			Gwylan looks away and fails to make eye contact for the next several minutes.
		<</if>>
	<<else>>
		You put the bowl to your lips, and drink half of the fluid, <span class="lewd">absorbing the poison</span>.
		<<if $angel gte 6>>
			<span class="gold">The purity within you clashes with it, snuffing it out.</span><<trauma _traumaFactor>><<pain 1>><<gtrauma>><<gpain>>
		<<elseif $fallenangel gte 2 and $fallenangel lt 4>>
			<span class="black">It rushes to fill the emptiness inside of you, and vanishes within. You feel nothing.</span>
		<<elseif $demon gte 6>>
			<span class="purple">It melds with your very being.</span><<stress `(_stressFactor * -1)`>><<trauma `(_traumaFactor * -1)`>><<purity `(_purityFactor * 2)`>><<llstress>><<ltrauma>><<lllpurity>>
		<<elseif $dryad gte 6>>
			<span cass="red">You feel violently ill as it twists your connection to the world. Your blossom turns sickly for a moment.</span><<stress _stressFactor>><<trauma _traumaFactor>><<pain 10>><<ggstress>><<ggtrauma>><<ggpain>>
		<<else>>
			<<purity _purityFactor>><<llpurity>>
		<</if>>
		<br><br>

		Gwylan drinks the other half, and wipes <<his>> mouth. <<He>> shudders. "You're too kind, dear."
	<</if>>
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("ritual_corruption_share")>>
<<link [[Relax and chat with Gwylan|Gwylan Ritual Bait Corruption Relax]]>><</link>>
