:: Gwylan Ritual Bait Corruption Relax
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>

<<if !$beastRitual.sharedBurden and $beastRitual.lure isnot "dryad" and $phase isnot 1>>
	Gwylan downs the glowing fluid.
	<br><br>

	<<if $beastRitual.poisonAmount gte 5>>
		After a moment, <span class="red"><<he>> clutches <<his>> stomach and lies on <<his>> side</span>. You rub <<his>> back. <<npcincr Gwylan dom -3>><<llyearning>>
	<<elseif $beastRitual.poisonAmount gte 3>>
		After a moment, <span class="pink"><<he>> doubles over,</span> but manages to steady <<himself>>. <<npcincr Gwylan dom -2>><<lyearning>>
	<<elseif $beastRitual.poisonAmount gte 1>>
		After a moment, <span class="purple"><<he>> clutches <<his>> stomach,</span> but quickly steadies <<himself>>. <<npcincr Gwylan dom -1>><<lyearning>>
	<<else>>
		After a moment, <span class="blue"><<he>> winces,</span> but quickly composes <<himself>>.
	<</if>>
	<br><br>
<</if>>

You spend some time relaxing in the garden with <<him>>.
<<if $gwylan.wary gt 1 and $beastRitual.purge gte 1>>
	<<set $gwylan.wary -= 1>>
	<<if $gwylan.wary lte 1>>
		<<set $gwylan.forgiven to true>>
	<<else>>
		<span class="green"><<He>> seems to let <<his>> guard down.</span> <<glove>>
	<</if>>
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<He>> eventually stands up.
<<if $gwylan.forgiven>>
	<<run delete $gwylan.forgiven>>
	<<He>> stares through you.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Look away|Gwylan Ritual Forgive]]>><<set $phase to 1>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Stare back|Gwylan Ritual Forgive]]>><<set $phase to 2>><</link>>
	<br>
<<else>>
	<br><br>
	<<link [[Next|Gwylan Ritual Bait Exit]]>><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>

:: Gwylan Ritual Bait Exit
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>

Gwylan ushers you back inside. <<He>> enters the shop again <<himself>> a few minutes later.
<br><br>

<<if $beastRitual.fallen>>
	<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("fallen_fault")>>
<</if>>
<<unset $beastRitual>>
<<run delete $gwylan.ritualMissed>><<run delete $gwylan.ritualNext>>
<<set $gwylan.timer.ritual to new DateTime(Time.date).addDays(7).timeStamp>>
<<set $gwylan.hunting to 0>>
<<set $gwylan.punishment to false>>
<<set $daily.gwylan.ritual to true>>
